org.jetel.graph.runtime.jmx

Interface PhaseTracking

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PhaseTrackingDetail

    public interface PhaseTracking
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface for the tracking information about a phase. This interface should be used by JMX clients. TODO: currently the start and endtime is used by all clients only to calculate exec time - refactor. Each change of this interface (rename, delete or add of an attribute) should be reflected in TrackingMetadataToolkit class.
    Since:
    May 14, 2009
